    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "p02_fr_t",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 2141,
      "width": 1080,
      "height": 52,
      "text": "FR-16: Pass = Change Job & Comp → Event: Completion of Probation (COMPROB_COMPROB)\nFR-17: Extend = Change Probation End Date → system warning → Proceed (Event: DC_EXTPROB)\nFR-18: Fail = Terminate action → OK to Rehire decision → Transfer subordinates if any (TERM_UNSUCPROB)\nFR-19: Verify Pass Probation Date in Employment Details after completion",
      "originalText": "FR-16: Pass = Change Job & Comp → Event: Completion of Probation (COMPROB_COMPROB)\nFR-17: Extend = Change Probation End Date → system warning → Proceed (Event: DC_EXTPROB)\nFR-18: Fail = Terminate action → OK to Rehire decision → Transfer subordinates if any (TERM_UNSUCPROB)\nFR-19: Verify Pass Probation Date in Employment Details after completion",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
