    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "p03_fr_t",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 2870,
      "width": 1080,
      "height": 130,
      "text": "FR-20: Direct Edit sections: National ID, Biographical, Contact, Address, Emergency Contact, Work Permit\nFR-21: Historical Edit (with effective date): Personal Info, Dependents, Payment Info\nFR-22: Change Job & Comp required for: Org Info, Job Info, Job Relationships, Compensation\nFR-23: Alt Cost Distribution via Take Action → Manage Alt Cost Distribution (must sum to 100%)\nFR-24: Workflow-triggering fields: First Name, Last Name, Name TH/EN, Marital Status, Military, Address\nFR-25: Employee Profile (Background Elements): Education, Work Exp, Salary History, Certifications, etc.\nFR-26: Pay Rate Change: Actions → Change Job & Comp → Use Change Calculator (amount or %)\nFR-27: Mass Upload: 2-file import (CompInfoImportTemplate.csv + PayComponentRecurringImportTemplate.csv)\nFR-28: Mass Upload: Purge Type = Incremental, Date = dd/MM/yyyy, Encoding = UTF-8\nFR-29: Future-dated record blocks backdated insert → must delete future record first",
      "originalText": "FR-20: Direct Edit sections: National ID, Biographical, Contact, Address, Emergency Contact, Work Permit\nFR-21: Historical Edit (with effective date): Personal Info, Dependents, Payment Info\nFR-22: Change Job & Comp required for: Org Info, Job Info, Job Relationships, Compensation\nFR-23: Alt Cost Distribution via Take Action → Manage Alt Cost Distribution (must sum to 100%)\nFR-24: Workflow-triggering fields: First Name, Last Name, Name TH/EN, Marital Status, Military, Address\nFR-25: Employee Profile (Background Elements): Education, Work Exp, Salary History, Certifications, etc.\nFR-26: Pay Rate Change: Actions → Change Job & Comp → Use Change Calculator (amount or %)\nFR-27: Mass Upload: 2-file import (CompInfoImportTemplate.csv + PayComponentRecurringImportTemplate.csv)\nFR-28: Mass Upload: Purge Type = Incremental, Date = dd/MM/yyyy, Encoding = UTF-8\nFR-29: Future-dated record blocks backdated insert → must delete future record first",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
