    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "bw03a_rules_t",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 3251,
      "width": 1080,
      "height": 65,
      "text": "BR-17: Direct Edit sections: National ID, Biographical, Contact, Address, Emergency, Work Permit, Profile\nBR-18: Historical Edit (ต้อง effective date): Personal Info, Dependents, Payment Info\nBR-19: Change Job & Comp required สำหรับ: Org Info, Job Info, Compensation, Job Relationships\nBR-20: Workflow triggers อัตโนมัติเมื่อแก้: First Name, Last Name, Name TH, Marital Status, Military, Address\nBR-21: Alt Cost Distribution ต้อง sum = 100% เสมอ",
      "originalText": "BR-17: Direct Edit sections: National ID, Biographical, Contact, Address, Emergency, Work Permit, Profile\nBR-18: Historical Edit (ต้อง effective date): Personal Info, Dependents, Payment Info\nBR-19: Change Job & Comp required สำหรับ: Org Info, Job Info, Compensation, Job Relationships\nBR-20: Workflow triggers อัตโนมัติเมื่อแก้: First Name, Last Name, Name TH, Marital Status, Military, Address\nBR-21: Alt Cost Distribution ต้อง sum = 100% เสมอ",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#dc2626",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
