    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "p04_fr_t",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 4328,
      "width": 1080,
      "height": 156,
      "text": "FR-30: Transfer within Co (no SSO change): Event = Transfer, Reason = TRN_TRNWICNSO\nFR-31: Transfer within Co (SSO change): TRN_TRNWICWSO → additional Compensation step (update Pay Group)\nFR-32: Promotion: Event = Promotion, Reason = PRM_PRM | Demotion: PRM_DEMO\nFR-33: Transfer across Company = Terminate at source + Hire at destination (not just Change Job)\nFR-34: Payroll Period Lock: Effective Date locked to period start (01.mm or 21.mm)\nFR-35: Acting = Concurrent Employment: secondary = Yes, Pay Group = 99 (Non-PY relevant)\nFR-36: End Acting: Terminate selected assignment (NOT 'All Employments'), TERM_ENDASSIGN\nFR-37: Change Employee Type: JCHG_EMPTYPE → if Pay Group changes → DC_CHGINPAY\nFR-38: FTE reduction → Standard Weekly Hours auto-adjust proportionally\nFR-39: Suspension: unique path via Employment Info → Job Info → History → Insert New Record\nFR-40: Must Insert Return record (not delete Suspension) for audit trail\nFR-41: Position unchanged during suspension period",
      "originalText": "FR-30: Transfer within Co (no SSO change): Event = Transfer, Reason = TRN_TRNWICNSO\nFR-31: Transfer within Co (SSO change): TRN_TRNWICWSO → additional Compensation step (update Pay Group)\nFR-32: Promotion: Event = Promotion, Reason = PRM_PRM | Demotion: PRM_DEMO\nFR-33: Transfer across Company = Terminate at source + Hire at destination (not just Change Job)\nFR-34: Payroll Period Lock: Effective Date locked to period start (01.mm or 21.mm)\nFR-35: Acting = Concurrent Employment: secondary = Yes, Pay Group = 99 (Non-PY relevant)\nFR-36: End Acting: Terminate selected assignment (NOT 'All Employments'), TERM_ENDASSIGN\nFR-37: Change Employee Type: JCHG_EMPTYPE → if Pay Group changes → DC_CHGINPAY\nFR-38: FTE reduction → Standard Weekly Hours auto-adjust proportionally\nFR-39: Suspension: unique path via Employment Info → Job Info → History → Insert New Record\nFR-40: Must Insert Return record (not delete Suspension) for audit trail\nFR-41: Position unchanged during suspension period",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 2277,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 2278,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": null,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": "p04_fr_bg",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
