    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "eg_t",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 8425,
      "width": 880,
      "height": 70,
      "text": "A=Permanent | W=Expat Outbound | C=Expat Inbound | D=Retirement | E=Temporary | F=DVT | G=Internship | H=Contingent\nSubgroups: Permanent/Expat 07-27 | Temp: P1(Monthly) P2(Piecework) P3(Daily) | DVT: D1/D2 | Intern: T1/T2 | C1=Consultant\nPiecework: X7-XB | Daily: Y7-YB\nContract Types: Regular | Contract-Monthly | Contract-Yearly | Contract-Long term",
      "originalText": "A=Permanent | W=Expat Outbound | C=Expat Inbound | D=Retirement | E=Temporary | F=DVT | G=Internship | H=Contingent\nSubgroups: Permanent/Expat 07-27 | Temp: P1(Monthly) P2(Piecework) P3(Daily) | DVT: D1/D2 | Intern: T1/T2 | C1=Consultant\nPiecework: X7-XB | Daily: Y7-YB\nContract Types: Regular | Contract-Monthly | Contract-Yearly | Contract-Long term",
